ts liegt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aLiterature, MedievalxHistory and criticism. 0aMiddle AgesxHistoriography. 0aTrojans in literature. 70(DE-588)4020531-90(DE-627)1045643260(DE-576)208933751aGeschichtsschreibung2gnd 70(DE-588)4049716-10(DE-627)1046751520(DE-576)209083182aRezeption2gnd 70(DE-588)4060976-50(DE-627)1061376460(DE-576)209137460aTrojanischer Krieg2gnd 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Geschichte 2005-2012z9783110346787oZDB-23-OGS0 cprintz978305004580140uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978305004866640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783050048666423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783050048666/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OGSc2005d2012